The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The function modifies its value parameters 'buffer_size' and 'push_data' (buffer_size = MHD_SCKT_SEND_MAX_SIZE_; push_data = false;). Rule 17.8 forbids modifying function parameters, so this is a violation. Use local copies (e.g. size_t local_buffer_size = buffer_size; bool local_push_data = push_data;) and modify those instead to comply.
</scenario>

